NAME
    hsh - simple shell command interpreter

SYNOPSIS
    ./hsh

DESCRIPTION
    hsh is a basic UNIX command language interpreter. It reads commands from the standard input and executes them.

FEATURES
    * Path Resolution: Automatically searches the PATH environment variable.
    * Error Handling: Prints standard error messages for commands not found.

BUILT-IN COMMANDS
    env
        Prints the complete list of current environment variables.

    exit
        Terminates the shell.

